Resource Profile: ILCore Practitioner Profile

Official URL: http://fhir.health.gov.il/StructureDefinition/il-core-practitioner Version: 4.1.0
Draft as of 2021-03-04 Responsible: Israeli Ministry of Health Computable Name: ILCorePractitioner

Proposed constraints and extensions on the Practitioner Resource

Usage:

  • Refer to this Resource Profile:
  • Examples for this Resource Profile: Practitioner/anesthesiologist-with-expertise, Practitioner/practitioner-md, Practitioner/practitioner-nurse, Practitioner/practitioner-psychologist

Summary

Mandatory: 5 elements (21 nested mandatory elements)
Must-Support: 7 elements
Fixed Value: 12 elements

Structures

This structure refers to these other structures:

  • ILCore Address Profile (http://fhir.health.gov.il/StructureDefinition/il-core-address)

Extensions

This structure refers to these extensions:

  • http://fhir.health.gov.il/StructureDefinition/ext-qualification-practice

Slices

This structure defines the following Slices:

  • The element Practitioner.identifier is sliced based on the value of pattern:$this
  • The element Practitioner.qualification is sliced based on the values of value:code.coding.system, value:code.coding.code
